query:
UPDATE task_template_groups
               SET name = $2, parent_group_id = $3, updated_at = datetime('now', 'subsec')
               WHERE id = $1
               RETURNING 
                   id as "id!: Uuid", 
                   name,
                   parent_group_id as "parent_group_id: Uuid",
                   created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>", 
                   updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
